# YouTube → transcript (Transcript mode "YouTube link" option) is served by the
# supadata-proxy edge function, which holds the Supadata key server-side. There
# is NO VITE_ var for it — set it as a Supabase secret and deploy the function:
#   supabase secrets set SUPADATA_API_KEY=sd_xxxxxxxx
#   supabase functions deploy supadata-proxy
# Get a key at https://supadata.ai. Without it, pasting a YouTube link returns a
# clear "Supadata key not configured" error; pasting/​uploading a transcript
# still works.
